description: Mobile Suite for Sweet Arleen's cupcakes & bread puddings and 2x winner of Food Network's Cupcake Wars.Sweet Arleen's has been just a dream of our founder Arleen Scavone...until now. After years of charming friends and family with these casual yet sophisticated treats, it really is a dream come true to share these favorites with you. Bakers use only the finest and freshest ingredients, incorporating seasonal fruits, Belgian chocolates, and harvest seasonings. There is no skimping or short cuts in Sweet Arleen's kitchen. Each cupcake and bread pudding is prepared to ensure an excellent product, each and every time. Sweet Arleen's boutique-comfort style ensures there's a satisfying treat for every palate, enjoy!
name: Sweet Arleen's
